  %h3 Icons
  %p You can also use icons within buttons.  You can combine these into a button group for a complete toolbar as well.
  .btn-toolbar
    %button.btn <i class="icon-eye-open"></i> View
    %button.btn.btn-inverse <i class="icon-refresh"></i> Update
    %button.btn.btn-primary <i class="icon-pencil"></i> Edit
    %button.btn.btn-danger <i class="icon-remove"></i> Delete
  .btn-toolbar
    .btn-group
      %button.btn <i class="icon-step-backward"></i>
      %button.btn <i class="icon-fast-backward"></i>
